    "Open deep research systems with fixed pipelines rely heavily on human-engineered inference workflows to generate long-form reports.",
    "In contrast, DR Tulu-8B does not use a separate report-generation pipeline and autonomously decides the length of answers based on given task prompts.",
    "WebThinker (report mode) performs competitively on long-form benchmarks, largely due to its pipeline that iteratively drafts and edits answers after running its default search flow with the base model.",
